snippet.title: You are who you want to be! Your NO.1 VR social app! Let's Reborn!
snippet.description:
Capture the best moments, send messages, join group events and play immersive games with friends together!

You will find endless stream of virtual experiences that feel personalized just for you and they are all created by the players!
